<i>♪ With somebody who loves me ♪</i>

27:48.917 --> 27:51.479
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,
this is your captain speaking.</i>

27:51.503 --> 27:53.922
<i>We're making our final descent
into Heathrow,</i>

27:54.005 --> 27:56.675
<i>and we'll be touching down
in about 15 minutes.</i>

27:56.758 --> 28:00.095
<i>From all of us on the flight deck,
thanks for traveling with us,</i>

28:00.178 --> 28:02.472
<i>and we hope you enjoy your stay in London.</i>

28:06.393 --> 28:07.393
Morning.

28:07.769 --> 28:08.769
Morning.

28:10.730 --> 28:11.916
- I was going...
- I feel like...

28:11.940 --> 28:13.066
- Sorry, you...
- No.

28:13.149 --> 28:14.484
No, you.

28:15.402 --> 28:18.530
Uh, I was just gonna ask if, um...

28:20.115 --> 28:22.409
This wedding of yours, where is it?

28:23.034 --> 28:24.285
Oh, um...

28:25.120 --> 28:26.246
Um...

28:26.913 --> 28:28.707
Shoreditch, I think?

28:28.790 --> 28:31.459
Shoreditch, yeah.
That's very cool. Very hipster.

28:31.543 --> 28:33.461
What about you? Where do you go for yours?

28:34.879 --> 28:36.256
I have to be in Peckham at 1:00.

28:36.339 --> 28:39.300
It's at an old chapel where my parents
used to do amateur dramatics.

28:39.384 --> 28:41.344
Well, at least you have till 1:00.

28:41.428 --> 28:44.013
- My ceremony starts at noon, so...
- Noon?

28:44.848 --> 28:46.599
Not the reaction I needed.

28:46.683 --> 28:47.683
You should be fine.

28:48.393 --> 28:49.269
If you hurry.

28:49.352 --> 28:51.062
And customs goes smoothly.

28:51.146 --> 28:52.939
Oh man.

28:54.899 --> 28:57.444
Cumulus clouds. Best clouds ever.

28:59.237 --> 29:02.449
They're the only thing on this earth
that looks like how you drew it as a kid.

29:02.949 --> 29:04.033
Hmm.

29:04.117 --> 29:06.828
So, your family's
not a collection of stick figures?

29:06.911 --> 29:09.038
- Mine definitely is.
- Okay, that I wanna see.

29:09.122 --> 29:12.667
Sorry, no meeting the family
till the fifth date.

29:12.751 --> 29:14.961
Says the girl
who slept with me on the first.

29:17.839 --> 29:19.549
I'm breaking all my rules for you.

29:21.509 --> 29:22.509
Me too.

29:31.394 --> 29:33.188
<i>UK passports to the left.</i>

29:33.271 --> 29:35.273
- Everyone else to the right.
- Ready?

29:35.356 --> 29:36.900
UK passports to the left.

29:36.983 --> 29:38.276
All others to the right.

29:38.359 --> 29:39.652
UK passports to the left.

29:39.736 --> 29:41.154
Everyone else to the right.

29:42.155 --> 29:43.364
Sir, ma'am,

29:44.032 --> 29:45.492
I need you to keep moving.

29:45.575 --> 29:47.118
- Give me your phone.
- Okay.

29:47.202 --> 29:50.042
- Sir, can't have you holding up the line.
- Sorry. I'll be two seconds.

29:50.121 --> 29:52.433
- This is my number.
- UK passports to the left.

29:52.457 --> 29:54.310
- All others, right.
- Text me so I've got yours.

29:54.334 --> 29:55.334
Sir, now.

29:55.376 --> 29:56.628
- Cool.
- Yeah, I'm going.

29:57.170 --> 29:59.255
Yep. I'll see you on the other side.

29:59.339 --> 30:00.339
Wait. What?

30:00.381 --> 30:01.925
See you on the other side.

30:02.008 --> 30:03.051
Okay.

30:03.134 --> 30:05.345
It's not like the lines
lead to separate countries.

30:07.180 --> 30:08.598
Oh shit.

30:14.771 --> 30:15.939
Next, please.

30:24.781 --> 30:25.865
Next!

30:30.245 --> 30:31.496
Next, please.

30:34.791 --> 30:35.791
Next!

30:38.169 --> 30:39.921
- Morning, madam.
- Um, morning.

30:40.713 --> 30:41.798
Hi. Sorry.

30:42.632 --> 30:43.632
Um...

30:44.008 --> 30:46.010
- There.
- What brings you to London?

30:46.094 --> 30:47.262
Uh, a wedding.

30:47.345 --> 30:48.847
And how long will you be staying?

30:48.930 --> 30:50.348
Uh, just the weekend.

30:51.182 --> 30:53.059
And did you get his name or number?

30:55.270 --> 30:56.271
What?

30:56.354 --> 30:58.606
Of the person you're staying with.

31:00.275 --> 31:01.985
Oh, yeah, um...

31:02.068 --> 31:02.986
Andrew Sullivan.

31:03.069 --> 31:03.903
He's my dad.

31:03.987 --> 31:07.615
We're gonna be at the, uh, Spits...
Spitalfield Hotel for the wedding.

31:07.699 --> 31:09.760
That's where we're staying.
My dad's getting married.

31:09.784 --> 31:10.785
Enjoy your trip.

31:28.303 --> 31:30.305
<i>♪ Running water ♪</i>

31:31.389 --> 31:34.559
<i>♪ Like a moment, slips ♪</i>

31:34.642 --> 31:37.020
<i>♪ Through my fingers ♪</i>

31:37.604 --> 31:40.481
<i>♪ Missed connection, passing ships ♪</i>

31:40.565 --> 31:42.775
<i>♪ In the same city ♪</i>

31:43.693 --> 31:46.779
<i>♪ With all these strangers in between ♪</i>

31:53.244 --> 31:55.163
<i>♪ Every corner ♪</i>

31:56.331 --> 31:58.458
