35:08.689 --> 35:11.651
<i>It lasted 52 minutes and 18 seconds.</i>

35:11.734 --> 35:13.903
<i>There were 760 flowers,</i>

35:13.986 --> 35:15.404
<i>five bridesmaids,</i>

35:15.488 --> 35:17.532
